feat(sprint3): role-based dashboards, member portal & ODPC consent UI

Implements Sprint 3 frontend for the Beba SACCO platform: admin
financial dashboard, member portal with repayment calendar, FOSA/BOSA
statement viewer with server-side PDF download, and ODPC-compliant
consent modal gate.

NEW FILES

lib/sprint3-api.ts
  - Typed fetch-based API client (no axios dependency) matching the
    existing import-api.ts pattern (localStorage token + tenantId)
  - dashboardApi: getStats(), getReports()
  - financialImportApi: preview(file, sheetType), execute(file, sheetType)
  - statementApi: getFosa(params), getBosa(params), downloadPdf(type, params)
    downloadPdf uses fetch+blob to stream PDF with auth headers, then
    triggers browser download via URL.createObjectURL  no token in URL
  - securityApi: getConsents(), checkConsents(), acceptConsent(type),
    listSessions(), revokeSession(id)
  - Full TypeScript interfaces: DashboardStats, DashboardReports,
    FosaStatement, BosaStatement, StatementTransaction, ConsentRecord,
    SessionInfo, FinancialPreviewResponse, FinancialExecuteResponse

