DESIGN DECISIONS

- No @tanstack/react-query dependency added; uses useState/useEffect
  with async/await matching existing codebase pattern
- No recharts dependency added; custom CSS bar chart used in reports
  (avoids bundle size increase; recharts can be added in Phase 4)
- PDF download uses fetch+blob pattern (not direct URL) to include
  Authorization and X-Tenant-ID headers securely
- All API calls use the same apiFetch helper pattern as import-api.ts
  (localStorage accessToken + tenantId, no global state dependency)
- Consent modal is a local component (not a shared component) to keep
  the consent flow self-contained and auditable per page

DEPENDENCIES

- No new npm packages added to frontend
- Uses existing: shadcn/ui (Card, Badge, Button, Skeleton), Next.js
  Link, native fetch API

